dc_title_s: Addresses Fond du Lac County, WI 2010
dc_description_s: This point data layer represents street addresses for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Fond_du_Lac_Addresses_2010.gdb.
